In the file : PHPExcel developer documentation.doc (PHP EXCEL Version 1.7.0)

on page 28, we have :

 

$objPHPExcel = PHPExcel_IOFactory->load("05featuredemo.xlsx");

but it seems we should have :

 

$objPHPExcel = PHPExcel_IOFactory::load("05featuredemo.xlsx");

Kind regards,

gaps team
Thank you for pointing this out. I updated the documentation. Indeed this was an error.
